# ── Hugging Face / model artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────
# The trained classifier weights are hosted on Hugging Face Hub at:
#   https://huggingface.co/rajvishwakarmaNIT/disaster-message-classifier
# Run `python scripts/download_model.py` after cloning to fetch them into
# this exact folder. Only this subfolder is ignored -- class_map.json,
# which lives one level up in Disaster_Prediction/models/, is small and
# project-specific, so it stays tracked in git.
Disaster_Prediction/models/multi_class_disaster_model/

